\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8727438 RC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10033895\charrsid11682795 Oh yes
, in the street. In fact I got a very sore heel once it almost kept me away from the choir treat because I - I'd walked on a bottle - a broken bottle. I must have the mark still. But - it's not unusual for boys to be in their barefeet you know. Oh quite a
 
normal - in fact you used to have a game who could make the biggest by - by - by banging our bare feet on the wet floor you can imagine how - how it would make a noise. Oh yes, it was - it was - me mother didn't like it. She thought that we shouldn't go o
ut in our bare feet but she did - turn a - a blind eye to it. She must have been pushed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12206039 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10033895\charrsid11682795 Would you have had secondhand shoes?
