He used to help us quite a lot. We used to get bathed in front of the fire - we had no bathroom. He used to help - he used to help an awful lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12206039 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10033895\charrsid11682795 Can you remember him doing these things?
