 a Sunday morning without my mother. So that she could - especially when he was working so he could get the - tea ready - dinner you see. He used to take me to - I remember him - he used sometimes go to his sister's on Sunday. She lives in 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Elizabeth Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. They were - I think they were the rich part of the family and - 'cos {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Elizabeth Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} in those days was very big. And he used to go to the public house at the bottom and he used to sit me on the counter and I always remember the biscuits and the cheese t
