No, like scrubbing floors or anything like that I don't think so but - I always had to look after my brother during the five }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1649205\charrsid11682795 weeks}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10033895\charrsid11682795  holiday. He was more or less - I felt almost felt like the old man of the sea.
