Oh, in front of the fire in - in what we called the back kitchen there's a back kitchen and a front kitchen and we used to bath
 in front of the - the - that was a ritual until - I - I - I discovered the baths and - tell - only about half a mile from where I lived you know. I - I used to get into more trouble going to baths unofficially than - because I used to be very keen on it 
but one of the big problems of course the baths was closed in winter but there were - there were - ordinary baths - ordinary baths in the baths that I used to go to at least once a week.
