ce puddings. And bread puddings of course sometimes. That was the old bread left over that had currants placed in them and somethi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11619784\charrsid11682795 
ng else with it, put in the ove}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10033895\charrsid11682795 n and - yes, nice and slowly, yes, oh yes, my mother was pretty good. Despite our poverty you k
