Oh well, if me father was working we'd have a joint you know a leg of mutton and my mother used to do - she'd do you very - very good with the stuff and that would be left }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11619784\charrsid11682795 over}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10033895\charrsid11682795  the next day. Round about Wednesday it would be sort of hash.
