Yes. My father was a great reader. One of the books - that was Jules Verne - the Jules Verne he used to read, yes. And one was in - The Wandering Jaw by Eugene Sild - h
e used to go mad over this thing - he got it from the library. I got it from the library years later. Dickens - used to love Dickens. Bleak House especially - oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12206039 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10033895\charrsid11682795 It's not a popular one either is it, Bleak house?
