Oh we always got weekly - newspaper a day. Magazines, yes. But I don't think they bought them - they just didn't have the money to buy them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12206039 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10033895\charrsid11682795 Would it have been an evening or morning newspaper you would have had?

