Oh evening. Very few morning newspapers taken by - in fact the Daily Mail I think 1912 it was a ha'penny actually fostered the habit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12206039 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10033895\charrsid11682795 Did your parents ever read aloud to each other or to you?
