might - it was high church - and evensong in the evening. And of course you used to go to Sunday school too. And then - every Wednesday and Thursday night had to go to choir practice you see. And - he was very - very, very - very very strict in fact even 
though I'd given up religion completely many, many years ago I still like hearing Stennings Crucifiction and Smart and Donoh - the religious - we used to sing all those.
