Well my mother didn't - my mother didn't - I don't think she actually believed in heaven - I'm almost sure she didn't, even - go back to 1918 - I was sixteen at the time. I believed in heaven at sixteen I think - I 
was just dropping away from it. So I suppose my mother at that time did. Yes.
