Why do you think she was like that - do you think it was because of her life before she }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15361118 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10033895\charrsid11682795  that she had been used to keeping in the background more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8727438 RC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10033895\charrsid11682795 
She came - she was of the opinion that the person of superior intellect - education to herself had superior intellect also. And she thought for some reason or other I can't fathom it yet that a person with a superior education is better that sh
e was. Who for no reason of her own didn't have as good a one. There's lots of people with the same ideas isn't there. They just can't understand it at all.
