Yes, without exception. There was another school, there was a - there was a - my sister went to it later on, it was sixpence a week to go there. That was
 a - a council school - Lister Drive council school. I think children were a little better off who went to that - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12206039 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10033895\charrsid11682795 
Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others?
